  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses wildfires.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>merges several funds into the Utah Wildfire Fund (fund);<hr><ltbullet>modifies references to the funds merged into the fund;<hr><ltbullet>addresses cooperative agreements with the Division of Forestry, Fire, and State Lands;<hr><ltbullet>modifies provisions related to the delegation of fire management authority;<hr><ltbullet>amends definition provisions;<hr><ltbullet>addresses elements of the fund such as what is deposited into the fund and how money in the fund is used;<hr><ltbullet>requires reporting;<hr><ltbullet>authorizes rulemaking; <hr><ltbullet>moves provisions related to community wildfire preparedness plans addressing wildland-urban interface; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming amendments.",
